text: Thomas Dick (20 May 1880 - 10 October 1938) was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1938 deaths Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dundee
